@startuml emergency_ingress_to_output_signal_flow
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

title Emergency Ingress To Output Signal Flow\n(TEST_SCN / Input_Console -> V2X -> ADAS -> CGW -> IVI / CLU)

actor "Emergency Source\n(TEST_SCN or manual inject)" as Source #F4F7FB
participant "Input_Console\nContext > Inject / Emergency" as Panel #E8F0FE
participant "V2X\ningress normalization owner" as V2X #E8F7E8
participant "ADAS\nproximity / alert decision" as ADAS #FCE8FF
participant "CGW\nwarning gate / decel gate" as CGW #FFF4CC
participant "IVI\nwarning render" as IVI #E8F0FE
participant "CLU\ncluster output" as CLU #E8F0FE

== Emergency Ingress ==

Source -> V2X : eth emergency alert\nor TEST_SCN compat dispatch
Source -> Panel : optional manual emergency inject
activate V2X
Panel -> V2X : Inject::emergencyActiveCmd\nInject::emergencyType / Direction / Eta / SourceId
V2X -> V2X : stageEmergencyIngress()\npriority rank / eta ordering
V2X -> V2X : publishNormalizedEmergencyIngress()
V2X -> ADAS : Core::emergencyContext
V2X -> ADAS : CoreState::emergencyIngressDirection
V2X -> ADAS : CoreState::emergencyIngressEtaSec
V2X -> IVI : V2X::v2xFrame
note right of V2X
Representative outputs
- Core::emergencyContext
- CoreState::emergencyIngressDirection
- CoreState::emergencyIngressEtaSec
- V2X::v2xFrame
- Core::timeoutClear
end note
deactivate V2X

== ADAS Emergency Decision ==

activate ADAS
V2X -> ADAS : normalized ingress seams
ADAS -> ADAS : calcProximityRisk(emergencyContext,\netaSec, speed, emergencyDirection, driveState)
ADAS -> ADAS : select emergency alert type/level
ADAS -> CGW : CoreState::selectedAlertDecisionLevel
ADAS -> CGW : CoreState::selectedAlertDecisionType
note right of ADAS
Emergency path highlights
- emergencyContext can override base alert type
- riskLevel feeds warning + decel decision
end note
deactivate ADAS

== CGW Effective Gate ==

activate CGW
ADAS -> CGW : decision seams
V2X -> CGW : timeoutClear / emergency context visibility
CGW -> CGW : selectedAlertEffectiveLevel / Type
CGW -> CGW : decelAssistReq / gate reason
CGW -> IVI : effective alert seams
CGW -> CLU : effective alert seams
note right of CGW
Gateway side effects
- selectedAlertGateReason
- decelGateReason
- fail-safe escalation if needed
end note
deactivate CGW

== Output Rendering ==

activate IVI
CGW -> IVI : selectedAlertEffectiveLevel / Type
V2X -> IVI : emergency direction / eta derived distance
IVI -> IVI : deriveEmergencyWarningCode()
IVI -> IVI : derive warningBeep / road flow / motion step
IVI -> CLU : frmClusterWarningMsg
note right of IVI
Representative outputs
- Cluster::warningTextCode
- UiRender::warningBeepState
- UiRender::roadFlowDirection
- UiRender::renderVolumeLevel
end note
deactivate IVI

activate CLU
IVI -> CLU : frmClusterWarningMsg
CLU -> Panel : warning text / state readback
deactivate CLU

Source <- Panel : Emergency ingress becomes visible\nas warning text / beep / render state

note over Source, CLU
Representative runtime chain
1. External or manual emergency ingress arrives
2. V2X normalizes type / direction / eta / source
3. ADAS converts ingress into alert decision
4. CGW gates decision into effective output
5. IVI / CLU render emergency warning to the driver
end note

@enduml
